      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Usp_CreateCrisNationalGridWestLinkedServer",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to create multiple linked servers in a Microsoft SQL Server environment. These linked servers are configured to connect to text files located on a network share using the Microsoft Jet OLE DB 4.0 provider. Each linked server corresponds to a different type of data file related to billing and payment details for the \"CrisNationalGridWest\" system."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Low"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure is straightforward, consisting of a series of "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "sp_addlinkedserver",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " calls to set up linked servers. There are no conditional logic, loops, or complex operations involved."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "3. Input Parameters"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "This stored procedure does not take any input parameters. It is designed to execute a fixed set of operations without requiring external input."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
